{
  "stem": "23096.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- if I knew then what I know now, I would have taken more details.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would wrote stuff down.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it's-- we didn't know what we were getting into.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know we were making history.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 11 SECONDS] So you know, hindsight's a lot better than foresight then-- so a lot-- lot of little details you don't-- you don't remember.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I can remember going back to Rome.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I knew where all the places were.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I didn't know how to get there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I'd been there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But even when I went back to Vienna, I went back to the house that I lived in-- well, it's not a house.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's like an apartment.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they don't have houses like we do in town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had to stand there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I-- I just closed my eyes and-- and tried to go back 40 some years, and just to picture what-- what I did when I came in the building.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because your memory sometimes-- little-- little things like that you don't pay no attention to, that you do every day.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So a lot of things about the camps and stuff-- I do remember that there were buildings along-- looked like a solid wall of buildings.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "There was no fence, per se.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was like the backs of buildings, with this big gate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Like I said, I don't remember any sign over the top, which they say every camp in Germany had this-- the sign, 'work will make you free,' [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But once inside the camp, these-- most of this stuff is-- it just burnt right into my brain.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was the shock-- the shock effect.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
